{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"782168230f49885740b191","title":"BUG-002：LVGL 内存重分配触发 Data Abort (os_realloc 越界读取)","desc":"","updated":1780371367062,"created":1780371330027,"custom":{},"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.BUG-002-LVGL_内存重分配_Data_Abort","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"38c962812d841c249c31a84a7c081b06","links":[{"from":{"fname":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机","id":"bk7252n-ai-printer","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":3,"offset":1706},"end":{"line":46,"column":58,"offset":1761},"indent":[]},"value":"项目.BK7252N-AI打印机.开发记录.BUG-002-LVGL_内存重分配_Data_Abort"}],"anchors":{"bug-002lvgl-内存重分配触发-data-abort-os_realloc-越界读取":{"type":"header","text":"BUG-002：LVGL 内存重分配触发 Data Abort (os_realloc 越界读取)","value":"bug-002lvgl-内存重分配触发-data-abort-os_realloc-越界读取","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"1-现象":{"type":"header","text":"1. 现象","value":"1-现象","line":17,"column":0,"depth":2},"2-原因分析":{"type":"header","text":"2. 原因分析","value":"2-原因分析","line":26,"column":0,"depth":2},"3-修复方法":{"type":"header","text":"3. 修复方法","value":"3-修复方法","line":50,"column":0,"depth":2},"4-涉及模块与文件":{"type":"header","text":"4. 涉及模块与文件","value":"4-涉及模块与文件","line":67,"column":0,"depth":2},"5-变更记录":{"type":"header","text":"5. 变更记录","value":"5-变更记录","line":76,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"lo6380sffe7882xxcsgnwby","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"bug-002lvgl-内存重分配触发-data-abort-os_realloc-越界读取\">BUG-002：LVGL 内存重分配触发 Data Abort (os_realloc 越界读取)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bug-002lvgl-内存重分配触发-data-abort-os_realloc-越界读取\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"bug-002lvgl-内存重分配触发-data-abort-os_realloc-越界读取-1\">BUG-002：LVGL 内存重分配触发 Data Abort (os_realloc 越界读取)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bug-002lvgl-内存重分配触发-data-abort-os_realloc-越界读取-1\"></a></h1>\n<p><strong>状态</strong>：已关闭<br>\n<strong>优先级</strong>：P0（系统崩溃 / 核心组件）<br>\n<strong>记录日期</strong>：2026-05-12<br>\n<strong>典型构建</strong>：<code>RT-Thread 3.1.0</code> / SDK 3.0.76</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-现象\">1. 现象<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-现象\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>设备在接收并处理 MQTT 下发的图片（<code>mqtt backend dispatch ws image to ui</code>），准备在 UI 上显示图片时，发生 <strong><code>data abort</code></strong>，随后系统 <code>shutdown</code>。</li>\n<li>崩溃时的寄存器信息显示 <code>pc</code> 落在 <code>memcpy</code>，且源地址（<code>r1</code>/<code>r3</code>）越过了 <code>0x02040000</code>（PSRAM 物理内存边界）。</li>\n<li>通过 <code>addr2line</code> 解析出的崩溃调用栈如下：\n<code>lv_timer_handler</code> -> <code>lv_draw_img</code> -> <code>decode_and_draw</code> -> <code>lv_mem_buf_get</code> -> <code>lv_mem_realloc</code> -> <strong><code>os_realloc</code></strong> -> <strong><code>memcpy</code></strong>。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-原因分析\">2. 原因分析<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-原因分析\"></a></h2>\n<p>根本原因在于 <code>beken378/rttos/mem_arch.c</code> 中的 <code>os_realloc</code> 实现存在严重缺陷：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token function\">os_realloc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>ptr<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">size_t</span> size<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>tmp<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    tmp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token function\">rt_malloc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>size<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>tmp<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">os_memcpy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>tmp<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> ptr<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> size<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// &#x3C;--- 致命错误：按照新分配的 size 拷贝旧数据</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">rt_free</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ptr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> tmp<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>越界读取 (Out-of-bounds Read)</strong>：当 LVGL 需要扩大内存块时（例如从较小的 buffer 扩大到 960 字节），传入的 <code>size</code> 参数是<strong>新的更大尺寸</strong>。</li>\n<li><code>os_memcpy</code> 错误地按照新尺寸 <code>size</code> 从旧指针 <code>ptr</code> 处拷贝数据，导致读取了超出旧内存块实际大小的数据。</li>\n<li><strong>触发 Data Abort</strong>：在本次崩溃中，旧内存块恰好分配在 PSRAM（<code>0x02000000</code> - <code>0x02040000</code>）的末尾附近。越界读取直接跨越了物理内存的最高边界 <code>0x02040000</code>，访问了未映射的非法地址，从而触发了硬件级别的 Data Abort。</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-修复方法\">3. 修复方法<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-修复方法\"></a></h2>\n<p>RT-Thread 内核本身已经提供了完善的 <code>rt_realloc</code> 函数，它能够正确处理新旧内存块的大小，并在可能的情况下原地扩容，避免不必要的拷贝和越界问题。</p>\n<p>将 <code>os_realloc</code> 的实现修改为直接调用 <code>rt_realloc</code>：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token function\">os_realloc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>ptr<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">size_t</span> size<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token function\">rt_realloc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ptr<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> size<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>这不仅解决了内存越界读取导致的 Data Abort 问题，还能提高 LVGL 图像解码时内存重新分配的运行效率。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"4-涉及模块与文件\">4. 涉及模块与文件<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-涉及模块与文件\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>模块</th><th>路径</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>OS 内存适配层</td><td><code>beken378/rttos/mem_arch.c</code></td></tr><tr><td>LVGL 内存管理</td><td><code>beken378/app/lvgl/src/misc/lv_mem.c</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"5-变更记录\">5. 变更记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#5-变更记录\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>日期</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>2026-05-12</td><td>分析并修复 <code>os_realloc</code> 越界读取导致的 Data Abort 问题，状态置为已关闭。</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Dendron/notes/bk7252n-ai-printer\">BK7252N AI 打印机</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"个人开发笔记","desc":"个人开发笔记（Dendron 多项目知识库）","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"e7a2abab31fd5da92a5ad2e013605349","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"